de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.message

Interface ResultContainer<T extends Data>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the transmission object, the type must extend the data marker.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ImMessageContainer, TnccsBatchContainer, TransportMessageContainer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultImMessageContainer, DefaultTnccsBatchContainer

    public interface ResultContainer<T extends Data>
    Generic base for a helper object to pass on a transmission result such as a message or batch and minor validation errors after parsing for further processing.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      List<ValidationException> getExceptions()
      Returns a list of minor errors, that occurred during parsing.
      T getResult()
      Returns the transmission result such as a message or batch.
